            <description><![CDATA[<p>Release date: 2026-05-14</p>
<h2 id="new">New</h2>
<h2 id="improvements">Improvements</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Made subscription sign-in more reliable.</strong> NameQuick
now handles more account details from the billing system, so active
customers are less likely to be asked to start checkout again.</li>
<li><strong>Improved account checks after checkout.</strong> Returning
to the app after starting a managed AI trial now handles existing
account access more carefully.</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="bug-fixes">Bug Fixes</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Fixed a bug where active subscription trials could fail to
verify.</strong> Customers with an active managed AI trial should now be
recognized correctly instead of seeing a connection-style verification
error.</li>
<li><strong>Fixed a bug that could mix up managed AI and self-managed
access.</strong> NameQuick now keeps self-managed provider choices
separate from managed AI subscriptions more consistently.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
